# React Native SSL Manager - Project Overview

This is a React Native library providing seamless SSL certificate pinning integration for enhanced network security. The main purpose is to protect applications against man-in-the-middle (MITM) attacks.

## Key Components

- **Main Library**: [src/index.tsx](mdc:src/index.tsx) - Core SSL pinning functionality
- **Android Implementation**: [android/src/main/java/com/usesslpinning/](mdc:android/src/main/java/com/usesslpinning/) - Native Android SSL pinning
- **iOS Implementation**: [ios/UseSslPinning.swift](mdc:ios/UseSslPinning.swift) and [ios/UseSslPinning.mm](mdc:ios/UseSslPinning.mm) - Native iOS SSL pinning
- **Example App**: [example/](mdc:example/) - Complete implementation example
- **Configuration**: Uses `ssl_config.json` files for certificate management

